<Content>Best place to stay for access to Children's Hospital Boston We just returned from Boston, MA, having stayed at this hotel for 10 days. Our son underwent surgery at Children's Hospital Boston and we needed accomodations near the facility. The hotel is less than one block away from the hospital, and within walking distance to many other attractions as well as the public transportation system. It is about a $30 cab ride from Logan International Airport. The front desk was kind enough to realize the length of our stay, and gave us a VERY spacious room along with complimentary crib for my son. With the exception of frequent ambulances (which can't be helped), the room was very quiet. Housekeeping was fantastic. The hotel is also conveniently attached to a mall food court, so we had easy access to multiple take-out options. There is a CVS pharmacy within the complex which was very convenient. The hotel offers an exceptional children's hospital rate, and then also reduced the rate because we had an extended stay. If we need to return for further medical care, we will certainly stay here again. 
